OL,3,CGuernsey Deputy estimates Aurgigny
OL,4,Clost several million in 2024
OL,6,FAurigny will have made a loss of
OL,7,Fseveral million last year if Deputy
OL,8,FPeter Roffey's predictions are correct.
OL,10,FIt comes after a string of unexpected
OL,11,Fevents for the state-owned airline in
OL,12,F2024, including three major tech
OL,13,Fissues.
OL,15,FDeputy Roffey, President of Guernsey's
OL,16,FStates Trading Supervisory Board,
OL,17,Fsays: "We know they had a fairly
OL,18,Fdisastrous year last year and they had
OL,19,Fto do a lot of wet leasing, far more
OL,20,Fthan they wanted to.
