OL,3,CGuernsey Deputy estimates Aurgigny
OL,4,Clost several million in 2024
OL,6,F"So I'm fully expecting there to be a
OL,7,Fseveral million pound loss. But they
OL,8,Fhad a very good year in 2022 and 2023,
OL,9,Fso they will not be asking the
OL,10,Ftaxpayer for any additional funds."
OL,12,FAn inquiry into the airline launched
OL,13,Fby the States Trading Supervisory
OL,14,FBoard found no negligence or
OL,15,Fmismanagement on the airline's part,
OL,16,Fjust bad luck.
OL,18,FJoe Mooney, a member of Guernsey's
OL,19,FAviation Action Group, believes the
OL,20,Fairline's current model is not working.
