OL,3,CGuernsey Deputy estimates Aurgigny
OL,4,Clost several million in 2024
OL,6,FHe says: "They had received #47
OL,7,Fmillion from the taxpayer in 2021 and
OL,8,Fanother #18 million in 2022.
OL,10,F"In the space of fourteen months
OL,11,Fbetween 2021 and 2022, we gave Aurigny
OL,12,Fa brand new school. When are we going
OL,13,Fto realise that the Aurigny operating
OL,14,Fmodel doesn't work?"
OL,16,FIn a statement, Aurigny says: "The
OL,17,Frequired auditing of our annual
OL,18,Faccounts, year ending 2024, has not
OL,19,Fyet concluded.
