OL,3,CGuernsey Deputy estimates Aurgigny
OL,4,Clost several million in 2024
OL,6,F"Once this process has been completed,
OL,7,Fwe will publish details on Aurigny's
OL,8,Fwebsite.
OL,10,F"Aurigny can confirm the underlying
OL,11,Ffinancial strength of the airline
OL,12,Fpersisted in 2024, however, a shortage
OL,13,Fof aircraft parts due to global supply
OL,14,Fchain issues materially impacted the
OL,15,Fbottom line.
OL,17,F"These are not expected to repeat in
OL,18,F2025."
